post_caption:
A long 2015 @ATPWorldTour season is getting to the end, a year with ups and downs, many experiences and challenges. After all I m really happy to finish the year among the Top 100 for the 8th time in a row!

Sometimes you win, sometimes you loose, thats sport, thats life, but never look back, look forward and enjoy every moment. I gave everything i could in every single match this year!

Thank you so much to my family, my friends, my team, my sponsors and of course to ALL OF YOU for the great support, I would never get that far without YOU! #BestFans 
It's time for holidays now, I will take some time off and recharge my batteries and come back stronger next season!

See you guys very soon, Rendy

